WEBVTT

00:00:00.036 --> 00:00:04.605
I didn't know when I agreed to do this

00:00:04.605 --> 00:00:10.285
whether I was expected to talk or to sing.

00:00:10.285 --> 00:00:15.333
But when I was told that the topic was language,

00:00:15.333 --> 00:00:20.104
I felt that I had to speak about something for a moment.

00:00:20.104 --> 00:00:24.453
I have a problem.

00:00:24.453 --> 00:00:26.467
It's not the worst thing in the world.

00:00:26.467 --> 00:00:27.664
I'm fine.

00:00:27.664 --> 00:00:29.413
I'm not on fire.

00:00:29.413 --> 00:00:31.314
I know that other people in the world